The paper also mentions the use of machine learning algorithms to recognize semantically equivalent cues of uncertainty. These topics are relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
